data.description: ***ALERT - Stop What you are doing and check this out!!  This home has an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN with a SUPER low interest rate!!!! Wait, What?!?!?! VA borrowers could be eligible for a significantly lower rate and obtain this home for a LOT less per/month than the average loan! Terms and conditions apply so give us a call for details and to pre-qualify for this rare opportunity! Agents, see PR for more information!*** This home has very motivated sellers looking to work with your offer! This home is being offered below market value AND above recent appraised value! WOW, where else are you going to find an opportunity like this!!! Give us a call to talk about making this dream sale come together! We can't wait to tell you all the wonderful things this home, and its owners, have to offer! If you want a home purchase where the things you want or need matter, where someone will be flexible, then look no further than this amazing home sale where WE want to make it a process that works for YOU too! Now, about this AMAZING home.....we just cannot say enough! This home grabs your attention the minute you walk into the custom front doors, and two story entry covered in heavy custom molding. The main floor offers you a guest suite, office/den, great room, full & half bath, dining room and renovated kitchen. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and newly customized cabinets with a massive walk-in pantry with additional refrigerator. Upstairs is a stunning master suite with a sitting room and spa like ensuite. Three more upstairs bedrooms and a large family room/loft are excellent for guest or a teen suite. The laundry is conveniently situated upstairs near bedrooms. The basement is ready to expand your home in so many ways! It is already stubbed for a bath and a kitchen, and has plenty of room for recreational space, or maybe a multi-generational suite! The possibilities are endless here! In the last 2 years homeowners have done updates that include 4 Lennox AC's, Wolf 36 in induction cooktop, Fischer and Paykel fridge, Bosche dishwasher, new exterior and interior painting and lighting, toilets, sinks, faucets, deck, fence, septic pumped and pump replaced, and much more. Let's not forget the very private drive back into the property and the gorgeous land that comes with this home. So many possibilities with 6.89 acres of gorgeous open land and wooded areas! Some inspections already done and passed...See documents for additional updates and improvements. Agents, please see private remarks for more information!
